@host = http://localhost:5077

### Register a user (writes the user + a WelcomeEmailRequested outbox row in one transaction)
POST {{host}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@demo.dev"
}

### Register another
POST {{host}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "bob@demo.dev"
}

### List users
GET {{host}}/api/users

### Outbox messages — right after a register ProcessedAt is null;
### within ~10s the background job stamps it (watch the console log the "welcome email").
GET {{host}}/api/outbox
